        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Inverse standard normal CDF. Three-branch rational polynomial, absolute error &lt; 1.15e-9 over <computeroutput>p in (0, 1)</computeroutput>. Behavior at the boundaries (p &lt;= 0 or p &gt;= 1) is unspecified — returns NaN or +/-inf. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
